# PII patterns for pre-commit hook (grep -E regex syntax, one per line).
# Copy this file to .piipatterns and fill in real values.
# .piipatterns is gitignored — real values never enter version control.
#
# Each non-empty, non-comment line is treated as a regex pattern.
# Patterns are OR'd together and matched case-insensitively against
# added lines in staged text files (.go .md .txt .json .yaml .yml .bat .sh .inf).

# IMEI (15 digits)
# 860000000000000

# ICCID (20 digits)
# 89000000000000000000

# IMSI (15 digits)
# 460000000000000

# Phone number (without +86 prefix, 11 digits)
# 138000000000

# Carrier-assigned IPv4 prefix
# 10\.0\.0\.

# Carrier DNS
# 114\.114\.114\.114

# Carrier name
# Carrier

# SMSC
# 8613800000000

# Carrier-assigned IPv6 prefix
# 2001:db8:
